'''Phantom Megalodon''' is a {{Rarity|Limited}} fish found in the [[Ancient Isle]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Phantom Meg is a spectral version of the ancient Megalodon, haunting the waters with an ethereal glow. Its serrated teeth remain just as fearsome, tearing through anything in its way. Though extinct for millions of years, this ghostly apex predator dominates the Ancient Isle and will challenge any angler brave enough to hook it.|Bestiary Entry}}

